description.narrative: The CIRCLE project provides technical, logistical and administrative support to USAIDs Health Research Program. CIRCLEs goal is to facilitate and support systematic research and research translation to accelerate Ending Preventable Child and Maternal Deaths, an AIDS-Free Generation, and advance other global health priorities. CIRCLE supports the Health Research Program to advance research-to-use processes through: stakeholder engagement; knowledge management to facilitate communication and collaborative learning; research translation; strategic planning; and targeted research and analysis activities.

title.narrative: CIRCLE Project (Coordinating Implementation Research to Communicate Learning and Evidence)
